channel.title: Leedle 317 - Custom Items | Creative Content | Reward System | Easy Bosses
channel.description:
[size=36pt]WELCOME TO LEEDLESCAPE![/size]
Leedlescape is a 317 loading 454, and is Delta Based. This is unlike any server you've ever played, mainly because of our custom pvm system and our customs themselves!
We have SO MUCH to offer, including a donatorzone, A CUSTOM POINT SYSTEM WITH REWARDS, 20+ custom bosses, 150+ custom items, 20 unique boss zones, a custom ::afk system and a unique home area. There are endless things to do on our server so come play today! SOME CUSTOMS:
Forums: http://leedlescape.freeforums.net Client: http://www.mediafire.com/download/mym7ikbchhznd1b/LeedleScapeV1.3.zip
What do we offer you?
- Exclusive donator zone with NPC's nowhere else located on the server - Custom leedle point system with cool rewards. - Over 20 custom NPC bosses. - 150+ custom items. - 15+ unique areas with NPC's - Afk system with unique objects such as a bench. There's way more for you to explore!
Here are some of the custom items we have: We have way more for you to check out!
* Supreme Claws
* Fusha Cav
* 20 Custom Bandos Chestplates
*Ghostly Bow
*Ghostly Guthans Armor
*Bankai Sword
*Farmer's Hat
*Bandos Full Helm
*Demon Head, Tail, Feet, Hands, Horns
*Zodiac Robes
*Butters Robes
*Beautiful Cape
*Dlord Legs, Chest and Cape
*Bandos WarSpear
*Obsidian Armor
*Ninja Armor
*Samurai Armor
*Bowsword
*Different types of Katanas
*Sword of Fear
*Danger Cape
*Dragon Cape
*Evil Dave top and bottom
*Tri-Godsword
*LemonLime Set
*Titan set
*Custom Santas
Here are some of the NPC's we have:
We have way more for you to check out!
*Big Swole
*Leeches
*Phoenix
*The Lion
*God
*Leeches
*Ogre Shamen
*Zygomites
*Rockgolem
*Gayboy
*Gnome Terrorbirds
*The Mummy
*Tiny Knights
*Spirit Crabs
*Zombie Monkies
*Anger Npcs
*Wyvern
*Shades
*Super Mourners
*Ghostly Vampires
We also have A BRAND NEW CUSTOM FAIRY ZONE! There are 6 new npcs located there, which you kill for "Fairy Points"! Each npc has a random fairy point reward ranging from 3-6, as well as their own individual drop tables. You can use the points you earn at the Fairy shop to buy awesome weapons and gear! Here are a few Fairy Zone Screen shots!
